iption"><strong>2.珂润浸润保湿化妆水（滋润型）        </strong></p><dir class="insert-outer " res-data-id="2813378"><span class="embed-card main-site res_smzdm"><span class="embed-card-logo res_smzdm"><img alt="男生如何开始零基础护肤~30+勐男平价护肤体验" class="res_smzdm" src="//qna.smzdm.com/202012/18/5fdcc8a8546b5527.jpg_e680.jpg"/></span><span class="embed-card-info  res_smzdm"><span class="card-name res_smzdm">日本珂润（Curel）润浸保湿化妆水III150ml滋润型（爽肤水保湿护肤女士补水适合敏感肌干皮花王原装进口）<strong class="price res_smzdm">158元</strong></span><span class="card-abstract res_smzdm"></span><span class="card-controls res_smzdm"><span class="mall-data res_smzdm">京东</span><span class="card-btn-deep res_smzdm">去购买</span></span></span></span></dir><p itemprop="description"><span class="img_desc"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/awx48onm/pic_24/' target='_blank'><img  src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202012/18/5fdcc1699868f7009.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" alt="这里拿错1型来拍照了，之前买错的"/></a>这里拿错1型来拍照了，之前买错的</span></p><p itemprop="description">这水很多人都懂，主打保湿，而且用了甲基葡糖醇聚醚-20，是一种玉米里面提取的葡萄糖，一种非常温和的保湿剂。此外还添加了消炎、舒缓成分的蓝桉叶提取物和尿囊素，达到消炎杀菌与舒缓去敏的效果，非常适合敏感肌使用，我自己使用起来的感受也是，非常的温润舒适，而且这个价格真的是没得说。         </p><p itemprop="description"><span class="img_desc"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/awx48onm/pic_25/' target='_blank'><img  src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202012/18/5fdcc169a86a37798.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" alt="      拿错1型拍照了"/></a>      拿错1型拍照了</span></p><p itemprop="description">值友推荐价：150ML 80元左右</p><h3>精华</h3><p itemprop="description"><strong>1.欧莱雅(LOREAL)青春密码酵素精华肌底液  </strong></p><dir class="insert-outer " res-data-id="2813374"><span class="embed-card main-site res_smzdm"><span class="embed-card-logo res_smzdm"><img alt="男生如何开始零基础护肤~30+勐男平价护肤体验" class="res_smzdm" src="//qna.smzdm.com/202012/18/5fdcc7f16e55f4762.jpg_e680.jpg"/></span><span class="embed-card-info  res_smzdm"><span class="card-name res_smzdm">欧莱雅(LOREAL)青春密码酵素精华肌底液50ml(女士面部精华青春密码黑精华修护补水保湿)<strong class="price res_smzdm">309元</strong></span><span class="card-abstract res_smzdm"></span><span class="ca